===Adverb===
'''telkens'''
# [[in each case]], [[each time]]
#: ''Telkens wordt hij herkozen.'' &mdash; He is re-elected each time.
# [[repeatedly]], [[time and again]]
#: ''Hij onderbreekt me telkens.'' &mdash; He's constantly interrupting me.

